Capital Markets

Company Overview of Arrow Investments Trust - Arrow Commodity Strategy Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Arrow Investments Trust - Arrow Commodity Strategy Fund is an open ended commodity indexed mutual fund launched and managed by Arrow Investment Advisors, LLC. The fund invests in commodity markets across the globe. It also invests in other funds. The fund primarily invests in commodity linked derivative instruments like swap agreements, commodity options, futures and options on futures to invest in commodities like energy, metals, agriculture, soft commodities, and meats. It seeks to track the performance of the Longview Extended Commodity Index. The fund was formerly known as Northern Lights Fund Trust - Arrow Commodity Strategy Fund. Arrow Investments Trust - Arrow Commodity Strategy Fund ...
Arrow Investments Trust - Arrow Commodity Strategy Fund is an open ended commodity indexed mutual fund launched and managed by Arrow Investment Advisors, LLC. The fund invests in commodity markets across the globe. It also invests in other funds. The fund primarily invests in commodity linked derivative instruments like swap agreements, commodity options, futures and options on futures to invest in commodities like energy, metals, agriculture, soft commodities, and meats. It seeks to track the performance of the Longview Extended Commodity Index. The fund was formerly known as Northern Lights Fund Trust - Arrow Commodity Strategy Fund. Arrow Investments Trust - Arrow Commodity Strategy Fund was formed on December 31, 2010 and is domiciled in the United States.
